OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright with hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine. Becoming warm for most
OL,7,Fplaces away from the coast, where
OL,8,Fcooling onshore breezes will occur.
OL,9,FLater cloud will thicken.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FGenerally cloudy with a
OL,12,Fchance of a few showers, these most
OL,13,Flikely across the Pennines, especially
OL,14,Flater in the night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,17,Fisolated mainly light showers, these
OL,18,Fmost likely across the Pennines early
OL,19,Fin the day. Temperatures will be
OL,20,Fnoticeably lower than previous days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
