OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fdry start then outbreaks of rain soon
OL,7,Fspread east. Tuesday sunshine and
OL,8,Fshowers, some heavy with perhaps hail
OL,9,Fand thunder. Wednesday mainly dry and
OL,10,Ffine before rain arrives later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
